    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f15",
    "text": "Brandon's first solo \u2014 Meridian brake assembly entry filed 4/12/2026. Marcus signed off on packet; zero corrections needed. Proud dad moment.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-04-26T10:55:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b2752ae8877a428399480a9bcc52fa40",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-04-27T10:55:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f20",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f20",
    "text": "Answer: yes, brackets fall under HTS 7326 and are on the derivative list from Presidential Proc 9980 (Jan 2020). Need mill test reports and MID.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-04-27T11:02:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bed4db59ffae1fecdf98ffc58713c9f2",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-04-28T11:02:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f21",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f21",
    "text": "Method: net cost method for auto parts (Article 4.5, USMCA). Auto vehicles have LVC/steel/aluminum requirements. Keep RVC worksheet + labor value ledger.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-04-28T12:09:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b6661e11726115f2e94b16c86b83c5d6",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-04-29T12:09:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f22",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f22",
    "text": "First-sale eligibility for GLS \u2014 requires bona-fide sale for export, arm's-length pricing, and price paid for goods sold for export. Need bill of sale + payment trail.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-04-01T13:16:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b8ff2abb4c78de1e741919b524a5055c",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-04-02T13:16:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f23",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185444f23",
    "text": "Prior notice for perishables: 4hrs pre-arrival for truck, 4hrs for air, 8hrs for rail per updated rule. Confirm with Maumee ops for the frozen fish shipment.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-04-02T14:23:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b11174ecabc8a6f8750678476c18479b",
